---
description: Dart/GetX naming — files, types, routes, JSON keys
globs:
  - lib/**/*.dart
alwaysApply: false
---

- Files: `snake_case.dart`; primary type **PascalCase**, aligned with file role (Screen, Controller, Repository, Binding).
- Routes: central constants; must match `GetPage.name` exactly.
- JSON: Dart names + `@JsonKey` — no raw `map['snake']` in presentation.

Detail: skill `naming` in `.cursor/skills/naming/SKILL.md`.
